revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yassins}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yassin'' is the 24802<sup>nd</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1004 individuals. ''Yassin'' is most common among White (47.21%) and Black/African American (36.95%) individuals.
